{{>layout/header}}
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/mainCss.css" />

<div class="search">
    <div class="search-container">
        <input type="text" id="search-input"  placeholder="검색어를 입력하세요">
        <button id="search-button"><h6>검색</h6></button>
    </div>
</div>

<div id="main-box">
    <div id="best-designer-container" >

        <button class="scroll-button left" aria-label="Scroll Left">&#10094;</button>
            <div id="best-designer">
                <div class="best-designer-title">Best Designer</div>
                {{#bestDesigners}}
                    <div class="photo-card">
                        <a href="/designer/{{designerId}}" target="_blank" class="photo-card">
                            <img src="{{designerPictureId}}" alt="디자이너 {{designerNickname}}"/>
                            <h6>[{{salonName}}] {{designerNickname}} </h6>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                {{/bestDesigners}}
            </div>
        <button class="scroll-button right" aria-label="Scroll Right">&#10095;</button>
    </div>

    <div id = king-container>
        <div class="mainbutton">
            <a href="/map" target="_blank" >
                <img src="/images/icon/free-icon-map-2204655.jpg" alt="Neighborhood-img"/><h6>우리동네미용실</h6>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="mainbutton">
            <a href="http://localhost:8081/kingofcut" target="_blank" >
                <img src="/images/icon/free-icon-hair-cutting-4614171.jpg" alt="KingOfCut"/><h6>King of Cut</h6>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="mainbutton">
            <a href="http://localhost:8081/kingofdye" target="_blank" >
                <img src="/images/icon/free-icon-hair-dye-4614130.jpg" alt="KingOfDye"/><h6>King of Dye</h6>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="mainbutton">
            <a href="http://localhost:8081/kingofstraightener" target="_blank" >
                <img src="/images/icon/free-icon-hair-straightener-4614216.jpg" alt="KingOfStraightener"/><h6>King of Straightener</h6>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="mainbutton">
            <a href="http://localhost:8081/kingofperm" target="_blank" >
                <img src="/images/icon/free-icon-perm-5498766.jpg" alt="KingOfPerm"/><h6>King of Perm</h6>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="mainbutton">
            <a href="http://localhost:8081/kingofclinic" target="_blank" >
                <img src="/images/icon/free-icon-woman-hair-7755222.jpg" alt="KingOfClinic"/><h6>King of Clinic</h6>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="mainbutton">
            <a href="http://localhost:8081/eventsale" target="_blank" >
                <img src="/images/icon/free-icon-coupon-1831669.jpg" alt="EventSale"/><h6>이벤트 세일</h6>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="mainbutton">
            <a href="http://localhost:8081/purchaseofproducts" target="_blank" >
                <img src="/images/icon/free-icon-cream-2634641.jpg" alt="PurchaseOfProducts"/><h6>제품구매</h6>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="mainbutton">
            <a href="http://localhost:8081/예약하기" target="_blank" >
                <img src="/images/icon/free-icon-next-8066267.jpg" alt="예약하기"/><h6>예약 바로가기</h6>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div id = recommend-container>
        <div id =ggul-tip-memo>
            <h3>HairHub에서 알려주는 오늘의 꿀팁</h3><br>
            <h6>매일 디자이너님들의 소중한 꿀팁을 공유해 드립니다.<br>
            오늘도, 내일도  HairHub와 함께하는 예쁜머리</h6>
        </div>
        <div id =ggul-tip-video>
            <video width="740"  controls>
                <source src="/images/video/mainvideo.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                Your browser does not support the video tag.
            </video>
        </div>
    </div>



    <div id="review-container" >
        <button class="scroll-button left" aria-label="Scroll Left">&#10094;</button>
            <div id="real-review">
                <div class="real-review-title">HairHub 리얼 후기</div>
                {{#realReviews}}
                    <div class="photo-card">
                        <a href="/reviewList" target="_blank" class="photo-card">
                            <img src="{{reviewPictureId}}" alt="후기 {{reviewId}}"/>
                            <h6>{{serviceName}}[{{designerNickname}}]</h6>
                            <p>가격: {{reviewPrice}}<br>별점: {{reviewRating}}</p>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                {{/realReviews}}
                {{^realReviews}}
                    <p>리뷰가 없습니다.</p>
                {{/realReviews}}
            </div>
        <button class="scroll-button right" aria-label="Scroll Right">&#10095;</button>
    </div>
</div>


<script src="/js/mainscript.js" defer></script>

{{>layout/footer}}


